body: "Docs-first hardening follow-up: extend direct test-runner detection so run-script wrappers (e.g. npm run test) are treated as test runners for sandbox-safety validation. Keep explicit PM_PATH+PM_GLOBAL_PATH overrides and scripts/run-tests wrapper behavior unchanged."
